                This app is a simple, easy-to-use loan calculator that helps you make informed financial decisions.
                Whether you're looking to buy a new car, a house, or just need a personal loan, this app can help you
                calculate your monthly payments, interest rates, and total loan costs.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3">
                <a href="/calculator" class="rounded btn btn-primary">Try It Out!</a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
                <div class="subTitle">Built with pride using:</div>
                <div class="hstack justify-content-center my-2">
